Sceliphron madraspatanum (Fabricius)
Sphex madraspatana Fabricius. 1781. Spec. ins. 1: 445 [Mala bar ; type in London ( ?) ].
Pelopoeus interruptus Palisot de Beauvois, 1805. Ins. rec. Afr. Amer., Hym., p. 50, pi. 7, fig. 5 [type in London (?)].
